snippet.title: Level Up Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Trailer for my latest flash game. Level Up!

It's a platform RPG thats got it all: Amnesiac Heroes, Warring Tribes, Shadowy Figures, Romance, Epic Quests but most important of all, a sense of humour. Oh and hundreds of little magical gems.
